Package: powergene
Type: Package
Title: Simulation-Based Power Analysis for Semi-Field Vector Control Experiments
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrea M. Kipingu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Andrea M. Kipingu <akipingu@ihi.or.tz>
Description: An R package providing simulation-based power analysis tools to support the design of robust semi-field vector control experiments. It includes support for random effects and empirical p-value extraction, and parallelized workflows.
